author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Porcelain tile cutting tips…I have to notch this 12x24 around the doorway. But I don’t need a wet saw for this cut. For example, I can make a 2 inch slice with the IQ saw or grinder then use the Masterpiuma to complete the cut. This tile fits perfectly.
